{
  "stem": "11174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that car-- the people that went with that car that was from work to go in to eat their lunch in our kitchen-- on the walk fell a bomb, a American bomb, a small one.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a couple of people got killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Their lungs were torn from the pressure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It didn't hit them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One hit a little bit with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The pressure of-- because it fell very close-- the pressure removed their lung.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A few our people got killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Engel, a very nice person, [INAUDIBLE] got killed then-- a few people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as far as-- not the little guys, but the big merchants were very, very correct in business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the Japanese-- they were lying, and they were backing out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because after they surrendered-- the army after the atomic bomb-- they had-- the law was, the American law, that they had to run-- go back to Japan.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they couldn't take only certain things, only money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sold a lot of big pearls and-- the pearls especially-- a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were doing-- buying [? their ?] businesses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, we were stupid enough not to understand the value of what is right and wrong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this is-- you always get smart later when you find out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't be smart enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you're lucky, you do the right things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you're not, you don't do the right things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they are cheaters, and-- and it's not a secret.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're not ashamed of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm backing out, [? it'd ?] [? mean ?] something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not the-- the Chinese.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is holy-- your word to them is so holy they wouldn't-- except some guys that they are bad people or a robber maybe-- I didn't come across.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
